    <abstract>Collection of materials of Kodaira Sōji 小平総治（小平總治）(1876-1935). The collection was donated to the Fengtian Library (Hōten toshokan), a library owned by the South Manchuria(n) Railway Company, in the end of 1940, see p. 1. It included 512 Rubbings, collected by Kodaira.</abstract>
